Unbox, Asset Tagging of EUCD (End User Computing Devices), Equipment and Peripherals;
Managing of SR, Hostname Creation, Provisioning and Deprovisioning of EUCD;
Imaging, Patching ND Software Installations of EUCD according to company standards;
